<dl id="n41196a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n41" href="#n41196a">N41 (VI.B.33)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n41all.htm#n41196a"> 196(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> changed a sovereign / 4 times</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Lewis Carroll was never driven half frantic on a station platform because he had to <mark>change a sovereign</mark> to buy a penny paper while the train was on the verge of starting. <small> Miss Isa Bowman, <a name="IBSL" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#IBSL"><cite title="source">The Story Of Lewis Carroll</cite></a>. (1899) 38-9</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
